cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.DS 

The paper discusses machine learning models and their adaptation to changing needs, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also proposes two sampling strategies to generate unlabelled sets of points, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper validates the proposed strategies in six well-known problems, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), or data science (cs.DS).
